notes:
Download python IDE from following link and install it before the workshop.

1) For windows x86 and 64bit os 
https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.7.2/python-3.7.2-amd64.exe 
2) For other os 
https://www.python.org/downloads/release/python-372/

Connect your PC with internet and  open command prompt window then You can install packages via commands such as: 
python -m pip install --user numpy scipy matplotlib ipython jupyter pandas sympy nose 
Where user is to be replaced your username 
Fully charge your laptop prior to workshop

This is a handson workshop
Event Duration: 6 hours
One kit will be provided per team. Kit will be given away after the workshop.
It is compulsory for participants to bring a laptop(one laptop per team) with the required software properly installed in it.

Do you find yourself wanting to be equipped with skills to build a new-age technology device that is finding application across sectors ranging from military to entertainment?
Drones have always awed people and wouldn't it be cooler if you knew to build one?
Register for our workshop where you can learn how to build a drone from scratch and embrace the drone paradigm that is taking over the world, quite literally!
Session 1: Basic knowledge about Drones, there working and technical connections
Session 2: Hands on, on kits of the expert.
